  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK215">
<l>ūruṇi nīrniṟain taṟṟē yulakavām</l>
<l> pēraṟi vāḷaṉ ṟiru</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wealth of that man of eminent knowledge who desires to exercise the benevolence approved of by the world, is like the full waters of a city-tank.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
